# Real-Time Robotic Arm Using Curiosity Nano

This project demonstrates a robotic arm controlled using potentiometers and the Microchip Curiosity Nano board.

## Features
- ADC-based analog input
- Software-timed servo control
- Custom PCB breakout board
- External 5V servo power supply

## Hardware Used
- Curiosity Nano (PIC16F17576)
- MG996R and SG90 Servos
- 10k Potentiometers
- DC Buck Converter
- Custom PCB

## Software
- MPLAB X IDE
- MCC Melody

